    "title": {
        "rendered": "How to use the View feature"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<p>The <strong>View</strong> button is available in the top toolbar in the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/wordpress-editor/\" data-type=\"helphub_article\" data-id=\"11284616\">WordPress Block Editor</a> and <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/site-editor/\" data-type=\"helphub_article\" data-id=\"15201243\">Site Editor</a>. It&#8217;s used to preview what your post, page, or site looks like with the current changes applied.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/wordpress-editor/\" data-type=\"helphub_article\" data-id=\"11284616\">WordPress Block Editor</a>, click the <strong>Save</strong> button in the top toolbar to keep your changes as a draft of the post or page you&#8217;re working on. If you&#8217;re in the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/site-editor/\" data-type=\"helphub_article\" data-id=\"15201243\">Site Editor,</a> click the <strong>Save</strong> button in the top toolbar to keep the changes you made to your site and the templates you&#8217;re working on. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now click the <strong>View</strong> button to see how your changes look on the front end for the post or page or for the site.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"51\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.35.31-AM-1024x51.png\" alt=\"View in the WordPress Block Editor\" class=\"wp-image-16133157\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.35.31-AM-1024x51.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.35.31-AM-300x15.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.35.31-AM-768x39.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.35.31-AM-1536x77.png 1536w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.35.31-AM-2048x103.png 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><strong>View</strong> in the WordPress Block Editor</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"41\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.34.51-AM-1024x41.png\" alt=\"View in the Site Editor\" class=\"wp-image-16133153\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.34.51-AM-1024x41.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.34.51-AM-300x12.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.34.51-AM-768x30.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.34.51-AM-1536x61.png 1536w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.34.51-AM-2048x81.png 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><strong>View</strong> in the Site Editor</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>When you click <strong>View</strong>, it will display a drop-down menu with various options to preview the page, post, or site as shown below:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.24.38-AM.png\" alt=\"View drop down menu in the WordPress Block Editor\" class=\"wp-image-16133120\" width=\"620\" height=\"365\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.24.38-AM.png 826w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.24.38-AM-300x177.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.24.38-AM-768x452.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Desktop</strong>: By default, the Desktop view will be selected. You can preview how your page, post, or site will look on a desktop screen.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"570\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.08-AM-1024x570.png\" alt=\"Desktop view for the View option\" class=\"wp-image-16133205\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.08-AM-1024x570.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.08-AM-300x167.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.08-AM-768x427.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.08-AM-1536x854.png 1536w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.08-AM-2048x1139.png 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Desktop view</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tablet</strong>: When this view is selected, you will see how the page/post or your site will look on a tablet.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.36-AM-1024x575.png\" alt=\"Tablet view for the View option\" class=\"wp-image-16133212\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.36-AM-1024x575.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.36-AM-300x169.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.36-AM-768x432.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.36-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.36-AM-2048x1151.png 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Tablet view</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Mobile</strong>: When this view is selected, you will see how the page/post or your site will look on a mobile device.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"573\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.52-AM-1024x573.png\" alt=\"Mobile view for the View option\" class=\"wp-image-16133223\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.52-AM-1024x573.png 1024w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.52-AM-300x168.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.52-AM-768x429.png 768w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.52-AM-1536x859.png 1536w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.50.52-AM-2048x1145.png 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Mobile view</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Preview in new tab</strong>: When selected, WordPress will open the page/post or the site in a new tab on your browser.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the Site Editor, you will see the following drop-down menu with the options <strong>Desktop</strong>, <strong>Tablet</strong>, <strong>Mobile,</strong> and <strong>View site</strong> which will open the site in a new tab on your browser.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.59.14-AM.png\" alt=\"View drop down menu in the Site Editor\" class=\"wp-image-16133237\" width=\"648\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.59.14-AM.png 864w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.59.14-AM-300x173.png 300w, https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-25-at-10.59.14-AM-768x443.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">View drop down menu in the Site Editor</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video controls src=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/files/2022/10/Screen-Recording-2022-10-25-at-11.09.54-AM.mp4\"></video><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Video showing the View feature</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group changelog has-very-dark-gray-color has-very-light-gray-background-color has-text-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"changelog\"><strong>Changelog </strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Updated 2022-10-25\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Updated screenshots and content for 6.1.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Added info for Site Editor</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Added ALT tags for the images</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Added video to show the feature</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Created 2020-08-22</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
